{"tid":592580,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"介紹份hea工比住青衣至荃灣既在學巴絲","createTime":"2018-03-14T10:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T10:00:50.000Z","uid":91418,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00e50b447222b8eb8fea9bf4020df186b0c69ca6","tid":592580,"uid":91418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"事關因爲我要轉長工既關係 所以要quit而家份工 <br />\n呢份工適合讀緊ive或者大專學生 住荃灣至青衣先抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我既職位係幫同事做野 所以我拍拍屎忽走咗去佢就會好忙好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為變相佢要做埋我個份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n工作內容好簡單 亦都好hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係跟番要求份數print文件釘起佢<br />\n而且d文件唔會一次過黎 會逐d逐d黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以當你印哂已經收到既文件 而又未有文件可以印個陣係free既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上你做功課溫書打機睇劇食飯傾電話都唔會有人理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時薪唔高 不過都高過m記 7-11 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我收開50per hour<br />\n要番星期一至六 放假跟紅日 同一dd既台灣紅日<br />\n工時1800點開始（我慣左早半個鐘番去打卡呃鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）星期六就1點半開工<br />\n收工時間係 你print哂野釘好哂就可以走 所以唔定時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早既就9點 有時好夜12點都會<br />\n不過12點鐘之後先走可以claim的士錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心hea工 適合學生做<br />\n有興趣既留tg"},{"pid":"1c69eea23454f57c12c4257225580647e5c931a2","tid":592580,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8f706dafbd35b398a67afe9dc1dcf66fc71f724","tid":592580,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"返夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n斷六親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023deb34eaae3cc323597f736ef03d56c8334079","tid":592580,"uid":91418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8f706dafbd35b398a67afe9dc1dcf66fc71f724","tid":592580,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"返夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n斷六親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"朝早番學 有乜計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab9547e41c56bbb3f89c927994716ecadbd3c73","tid":592580,"uid":91418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:28:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26597024fdb0a9b2346f361d4e0c7db2a3d88655","tid":592580,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"荃灣至青衣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁實際係邊"},{"pid":"7123a938ef7b76dfd0777ff596e8d38b4fa15cf4","tid":592580,"uid":91789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:30:37.000Z","msg":"星期三六要賭馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a075f642294fee5294b45d4deda565dfd9fe4c5c","tid":592580,"uid":91418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26597024fdb0a9b2346f361d4e0c7db2a3d88655","tid":592580,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"荃灣至青衣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 